{"tid":1743414,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"警謊的真心話 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-11-21T07:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T07:50:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96e4141a33ce8e23ec5aec01bb0c5dea3dc4b7e6","tid":1743414,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191121/large/1574245082_6f8b.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191121%2Flarge%2F1574245082_6f8b.jpg&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6amePGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=4002c8ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191121/large/1574245082_6f8b.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n警謊的真心話 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191121/large/1574234625_c767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191121%2Flarge%2F1574234625_c767.jpg&h=013dedee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十八號晚，十萬香港人自發撐理大學生，至深夜，遭警方抓捕。現場傳媒拍攝到的視頻中傳出至少四聲槍聲。為驅散人群，警方還出動了水炮。更令人髮指的是，警方居然開動兩輛小巴，以極高速衝向碧街的人群，據報有人當場斷手斷腳。還引發人踩人、人疊人慘劇。事發後有三十一人受傷，其中十七人傷勢相當嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n事後警方居然把用小巴衝撞人群的瘋狂行徑形容為戰術。謝天謝地，警謊這次終於說了真心話。我其實很擔心警謊謊稱汽車機件失靈，把有意圖的謀殺行為掩飾為意外。<br />\n<br />\n用汽車高速衝撞人群，這是甚麼「戰術」？這是無差別集體謀殺，是恐怖襲擊，如果這叫做「戰術」的話，那麼，這是恐怖集團才會有的「戰術」。<br />\n<br />\n警謊說了真心話，其實比說謊更可怕，證明他們已經連掩飾自己的犯法行為都不屑去做了。他們以執法為名，公開地、赤裸裸地犯法，而毫無怯懦，絲毫不擔心會受到法律制裁。是誰給了他們這種特權？<br />\n<br />\n在法治社會，警方的責任是使用最低武力，把疑犯制服，若他們犯了法，自有法律制裁他們。可是香港警察不但濫用私刑凌虐示威人士，更阻止救護人員施救，甚至向在現場施救的救護人員發動襲擊。這是光天化日之下的反人道罪行，是向文明社會宣戰。這樣一支警隊，若不解散重組，把犯法的警察送上法庭，香港永無寧日。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"2ee3443da5bc0742ea7b1096656633cb3708f84c","tid":1743414,"uid":156509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:43:13.000Z","msg":"真，推"},{"pid":"a7a08d6431c4a08e355f85e7fb0640bbc26a6dbc","tid":1743414,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:43:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee03e6bad17cdc9b63eea2ec0928e60a447a3b71","tid":1743414,"uid":156509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:43:37.000Z","msg":"警察=恐怖分子"},{"pid":"4fc301592ebfd53b084124a09d49753ff7aadc6b","tid":1743414,"uid":320680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:49:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母你隻 fake news 狗同藍絲有咩分別？<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kauyimmedia/status/1197174401734602753?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkauyimmedia%2Fstatus%2F1197174401734602753%3Fs%3D19&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6amePGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=271f1ccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkauyimmedia%2Fstatus%2F1197174401734602753%3Fs%3D19&h=e83585ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kauyimmedia/status/1197174401734602753?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"1b3a864faf7411f92290ade0f584634a56866d09","tid":1743414,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:50:49.000Z","msg":"我都奇怪緊香港人接受警暴程度係咪又上升左？"}]}